# Cross-origin isolation: required for SharedArrayBuffer, which the phazor
# audio engine needs to run as a thread in the AudioWorklet.
# `require-corp` (not `credentialless`): Safari can throw when handing shared
# wasm memory to a worklet under credentialless. Consequence: every external
# subresource needs CORS/CORP opt-in, and third-party iframes won't embed.
# That trade is accepted deliberately — the instrument comes first.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
